profile:
Incorporated in 1983, Santex Roofing is your ideal choice for all your roofing needs in San Antonio, TX. With an A+ rating from the Better Business Bureau, our experts understand the physics of your roof and provide you with only the best, making you feel safe knowing you have a strong and trendy roof. We guarantee all our works, and we use Owens Corning and GAF roofing materials so that our customers get the highest quality products available.

For more details, visit http://santexroofing.com/ or call (210) 520-9487

profile:
Vertical Limit Roofing is a company that specializes in re-roofing and the application of fiberglass laminate. From the last 20 years, we are in the roofing industry with a positive response from our customers. This experience allows us to work with great skill and techniques with the help of our professional workers. 

Working as a roofing contractor in Ottawa will satisfy our customers to give the best experience. We use quality of products which goes for long, and you don’t have to worry about the  roof.  Choosing one-time quality service avoids several times of repairing which sometimes make a burden on your pocket.  As an experienced company, we give importance to time and make ensure the work is done in a given time with no complaints. 

Services we offer:

Vertical Limit Roofing offers different functions according to customers need that not only includes reinstalling and installing of new roofing but also includes other services that are required by homeowner for a perfect home.

•    Residential facility
•    Chimney removal
•    Sheeting replacement
•    New construction
•    Rooftop snow removal
•    Ventilation upgrade

Why choose us? 

•    We offer 24/7 emergency service for our customers.
•    We are specialized in lifetime asphalt shingles.
•    We have thoroughly trained and certified professionals.
•    We are dedicated to quality and artistry.
